---
title: "US37 — Personalised AI plan suggestions"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>TrainScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>GeneratePlan
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>FitnessPlan · PlannedWorkout
  A->>B: tap "Suggest plan"
  B->>C: generate()
  C->>E: fetchActiveGoal(userId) + fetchFitnessProfile(userId)
  E-->>C: goal + profile context
  alt AI available
    C->>E: suggestPlan() (personalised)
    E-->>C: AI plan draft
  else AI unavailable
    C->>E: BuildPlanSkeleton (rule fallback)
    E-->>C: fallback plan
  end
  C->>E: insertPlan(...) + setActivePlan(...)
  E-->>C: FitnessPlan + PlannedWorkouts (active)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (plan active)
  B-->>A: personalised plan on Train tab
  note over E: suggestPlan via AiGateway → suggest-plan Edge Function —<br/>persisted via PlanGateway (RLS). Premium = personalised depth (US18b basic)
